# Change Log
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.
This project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org/).

## V1.5 - Olive Nickel - 2016-02-19

### Changed
- Disable asset and helper generation in `rails generate` command

### Added
- Add our test_helper.rb

### Removed
- Raise on missing I18n

## V1.4 - Maroon Lead - 2016-01-29

### Changed
- Updated Ruby to 2.3.0
- Defaults to Intercity-Next configuration

### Added
- Puma as app server

### Removed
- All capistrano related stuff

### Fixed
- Make sure we import the correct bootstrap-sass scss file

## V1.3 - Purple Mercury - 2016-01-26

### Added
- Added font-awesome-sass gem for including FontAwesome icons
- Added bootstrap_form gem that includes a bootstrap form builder

### Changed
- Add Ruby version to Gemfile
- Moved JavaScript partial from inside <body> to inside <head> in application.html.erb

## V1.2 - Black Copper - 2015-10-31

### Added
- Added NProgress-rails gem
- Added letter_opener in development

### Changed
- Passenger files are now added to .gitignore
- We now generate an application.scss instead of application.css.scss file

### Removed
- We no longer send mails to mailcatcher in dev

### Fixed
- Place the JS file in the correct folder
